189.3, 282.5, 1210.5]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1059.7, 1189.3, 1068.9, 1210.5]}, {"text": "4,727.8", "bbox": [1089.6, 1189.3, 1144.9, 1210.5]}, {"text": "FMC Agricultural Solutions", "bbox": [91.0, 1243.1, 351.3, 1271.2]}, {"text": "We earn revenue from the sale of a wide range of products to a diversified", "bbox": [91.0, 1280.9, 608.7, 1306.9]}, {"text": "base of customers around the world. FMC Agricultural Solutions’", "bbox": [91.0, 1304.2, 608.6, 1330.2]}, {"text": "portfolio is comprised of three major pesticide categories: insecticides,", "bbox": [91.0, 1327.6, 608.6, 1353.5]}, {"text": "herbicides and fungicides. These products are used in agriculture to", "bbox": [91.0, 1350.9, 608.8, 1376.9]}, {"text": "enhance crop yield and quality by controlling a broad spectrum of", "bbox": [91.0, 1374.3, 608.8, 1400.2]}, {"text": "insects, weeds and disease, as well as in non-agricultural markets for", "bbox": [91.0, 1397.6, 608.5, 1423.6]}, {"text": "pest control. The majority of our product lines consist of insecticides", "bbox": [645.0, 1245.1, 1162.4, 1271.1]}, {"text": "and herbicides, and we have a small but fast-growing portfolio of", "bbox": [645.0, 1268.5, 1163.0, 1294.4]}, {"text": "fungicides mainly used in high value crop segments. Our insecticides are", "bbox": [645.0, 1291.8, 1161.9, 1317.8]}, {"text": "used to control a wide spectrum of pests, while our herbicide portfolio", "bbox": [645.0, 1315.1, 1162.5, 1341.1]}, {"text": "primarily targets a large variety of difficult-to-control weeds. Products", "bbox": [645.0, 1338.5, 1162.4, 1364.4]}, {"text": "in the other category include various agricultural products such as", "bbox": [645.0, 1361.8, 1162.9, 1387.8]}, {"text": "smaller classes of pesticides, growth promoters, and soil enhancements.", "bbox": [645.0, 1385.2, 1158.0, 1411.1]}]}